<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Iniciar Sesión</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/axios/0.27.2/axios.min.js"
      integrity="sha512-odNmoc1XJy5x1TMVMdC7EMs3IVdItLPlCeL5vSUPN2llYKMJ2eByTTAIiiuqLg+GdNr9hF6z81p27DArRFKT7A=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    ></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-100">
      <div
        class="w-full max-w-md space-y-5 py-14 px-8 bg-white shadow-xl rounded-lg"
      >
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold mb-10 text-gray-700">
            🏷 STREET WEAR
          </h1>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-700">
            Bienvenido de nuevo! 👋🏻
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
            Por favor, inicia sesión para poder ingresar al sistema.
          </p>
        </div>

        <form class="" action="/api/auth/login" method="POST">
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="Email *"
            class="w-full p-3 mb-5 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-200 transition-all focus:outline-0 focus:border-green-400 focus:border-2"
            required
          />
          <input
            type="password"
            id="password"
            name="password"
            placeholder="Contraseña *"
            class="w-full p-3 mb-2 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-200 transition-all focus:outline-0 focus:border-green-400 focus:border-2"
            required
          />
          <p class="text-right mb-10 text-md">
            ¿No tienes cuenta?
            <a href="Registrarse" class="font-bold">Regístrate</a>
          </p>

          <button
            type="submit"
            id="btnLogin"
            class="py-2 px-3 w-full bg-green-700 rounded-md shadow-md text-white tracking-wide font-bold transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-green-500"
          >
            INGRESAR
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
